Her Studio London x Original Flex I 'Colorful Blossoms'
results.story: Launching as part of a capsule collection with the UK design agency, the Her Studio London x adidas Original Flex ‘Colorful Blossoms’ delivers a running-inspired silhouette made for little feet. A soft shade of blue is executed on the shiny mesh upper, accented with serrated white three-stripes and a multicolor floral-print tongue. Elastic no-tie laces and a webbing heel loop provide easy on and off. The sneaker sits atop a white EVA sole unit with deep flex grooves for a smooth, natural ride.

results.name: Superstar 360 I 'Black Teddy Bear Fur'
results.story: The adidas Superstar 360 ‘Black Teddy Bear Fur’ transforms the iconic shell-toed sneaker into a cozy slip-on made for toddlers. The upper replaces traditional leather construction with plush black textile that resembles teddy bear fur. adidas Trefoil branding decorates the woven tongue tag and leather heel tab, the latter accompanied by a patterned pull tab for easy on and off. The sneaker sits atop a solid white EVA sole unit, featuring a hexagonal traction pattern underfoot.

adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Light (Infant)
results.story: The adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Infants ‘Light’ carries a re-engineered Primeknit upper in a muted ivory finish, accented with a post-dyed monofilament side stripe that adds a see-through element to the sock-like build. The shoe is updated with UV-sensitive technology, meaning direct sunlight causes the Primeknit construction to become tinged in pink, while the side stripe reveals a dark amber hue. The lightweight build is mounted on a responsive Boost midsole, wrapped in a rubber cage for added support and durability.
